                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>13.70</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-63" style="width: 3.918em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.19em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.368em, 1003.14em, 2.325em, -999.998em); top: -2.184em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-64"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-65" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">13.70</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-66" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-67" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">L</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>13.70</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>L</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-6">13.70\ L </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                                   </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-68" style="width: 10.207em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>5</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>35</mn><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>0.04</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>56</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.196</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-34">\rm 5nKMnO_4=2nCaO\Rightarrow5\times\frac{35}{1000}\times0.04=2\times\frac{m}{56}\Rightarrow m=0.196\ g</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-35-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.196</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>100</mn></mrow><mn>0.5</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>39.2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-392" style="width: 11.232em;                                     <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 8 </span>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-43-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1.21</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-557" style="width: 7.256em; </span>

                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি দ্বি-অম্লীয় ক্ষারের&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>200</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>c</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi>M</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-573" style="width: 6.41em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.255em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1005.25em, 2.722em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-638" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">V</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-639" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-640" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-641" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-642" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-643" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-644" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">88.889</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-645" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-646" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">c</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-647"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.82em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-648" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-649" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>200</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>88.889</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">c</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-50">\rm 200\times2\times\frac{1}{3}=3\times\frac{1}{2}\times V\ \therefore\ V=88.889\ cm^3 </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 11 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি জারণ-বিজারণ বিক্রিয়ায় জারক ও বিজারকের তুল্য সংখ্যার অনুপাত&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-55-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>3</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-751" style="width: 2.2em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-61-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.6</mn><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.5</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.6</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.5</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.8</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-779" style="width: 13.568em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.5</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.09em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.092em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-791" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-792" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-793" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-794" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.928em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.76em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.9em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-795"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-796" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.6</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-797" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-798" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.76em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.9em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-799"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-800" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-801" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-802" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.5</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.93em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.928em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-803" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-804" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.8</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-805" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">L</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.6</mn><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>×</mo><mn>0.5</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.6</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.5</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.8</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-61">\rm \frac{3}{2}=\frac{0.6}{V\times0.5}\Rightarrow V=\frac{0.6\times2}{3\times0.5}=0.8L </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

</span>

                                            <span>Question 14 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-64-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi></mrow><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-840" style="width: 37.483em;                                 <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 15 </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>ল্যাবরেটরিতে দুইটি ভিন্ন রিয়েজেন্ট বোতলে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-75-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>H</mi><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-988" style="width: 3.653em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.982em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1002.98em, 2.461em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.747em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-994" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.2em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.225em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.139em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>H</mi><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-75">HNO_3 </script></span> এর দ্রবণ রক্ষিত আছে। একটির মাত্রা 0.4M এবং অপরটির মাত্রা 0.1M। <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-76-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.25</mn><mi>M</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-995" style="width: 3.467em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.833em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.83em, 2.386em, -999.998em);                                                 <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>5:2</p>
</label>
                                                                   </div>
                                        </div>

                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>

                            <div class="row question">

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কপার সালফেট ও পটাশিয়াম আয়োডাইডের বিক্রিয়ায় <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-104-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1399" style="width: 2.982em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.424em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1002.39em, 2.349em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1400"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1401" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1402" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1403" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1404" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1405" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.043em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.957em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>1</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-104">1\ mol</script></span> আয়োডিন তৈরি করতে কী পরিমান পটাশিয়াম আয়োডাইড প্রয়োজন?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-105-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>I</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>I</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1406" style="width: 17.297em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

</label>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি জারণ-বিজারণ বিক্রিয়ায় জারক ও বিজারকের তুল্য সংখ্যার অনুপাত 2:3 হলে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-17-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.6</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-168" style="width: 3.914em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.206em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1003.17em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-169"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-170" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.6</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-171" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-172" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-173" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-174" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.957em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>0.6</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-17">0.6\ mol</script></span> জারককে বিজারিত করতে বিজারকের কত আয়তনের সেমিমোলার দ্রবণ লাগবে?</p>

                                    <div class="row">

                                            <span>Question 6 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-23-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>q</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>q</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-218" style="width: 30.814em;                                 <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 7 </span>
                                                          </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>ল্যাবরেটরিতে দুইটি ভিন্ন রিয়েজেন্ট বোতলে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-28-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>H</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>l</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-299" style="width: 2.424em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-29-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.5</mn><mi>M</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-304" style="width: 2.833em;                                                 <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-36-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-385" style="width: 1.459em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.186em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.368em, 1001.14em, 2.325em, -999.998em); top: -2.184em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-386"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-387" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-388" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">L</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>2</mn><mi>L</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-36">2L </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-40-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-427" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.371em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1005.29em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-431"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-432" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-433" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-434" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-435"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-436" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1250</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-437" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                     <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9 </span>
                                                          </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>b</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x2192;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-449" style="width: 35.509em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 10 </span>
                                                          </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-49-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>H</mi><mi>C</mi><mi>l</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-543" style="width: 2.424em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.977em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1001.94em, 2.349em, -999.998em);                                     <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 12 </span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-57-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>20</mn><mi>m</mi><mi>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-606" style="width: 3.132em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>সম্পূর্ণ অক্সিজেন বিক্রিয়া করবে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-72-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-862" style="width: 0.658em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.535em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.641em, 1000.49em, 2.42em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-863"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-864" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.753em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-72">\therefore</script></span>&nbsp;উৎপন্ন পানি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-73-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>36</mn><mn>32</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>28.125</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.5625</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-865" style="width: 15.412em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 12.625em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1012.58em, 2.502em, -999.998em); clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.66em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-870" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">32</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.82em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-871" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-94">\rm \frac{W_{H_2O_2}}{M_{H_2O_2}}\times\ 2=\frac{W_{KMnO_4}}{M_{KMnO_4}}\times 5\Rightarrow\ W_{H_2O_2}=\frac{0.3}{158}\times5\times\frac{34}{2}=0.1614</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-95-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1126" style="width: 3.65em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.994em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1002.99em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1127"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1128" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1129" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1130"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.9em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1131" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">H<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1132" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1133"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1134" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">O</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.781em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1135" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.247em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-95">\therefore\ H_2O_2</script></span>&nbsp;এর বিশুদ্ধতা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-96-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.1614</mn><mn>0.3</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>53.8</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1136" style="width: 11.682em;                                     </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কার্বন পরমাণু সংখ্যা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-101-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>40</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>6.023</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>23</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>12</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>400</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>5.0192</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>18</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1195" style="width: 15.166em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 12.42em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.863em, 1012.42em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1196"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1197" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1198" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; </span>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-121-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0.2124</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>M</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1448" style="width: 7.42em;                                         <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বিক্রিয়াটিতে P এর একইসাথে জারণ ও বিজারণ ঘটেছে। তাই, একে অসামঞ্জস্যতা বিক্রিয়া বলে।</p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                    <div class="input-group-prepend">
                        <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                        <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>1</p>
</label>
                        <span class="fas fa-check"></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-203-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mrow><mo>[</mo><msup><mi>H</mi><mo>+</mo></msup><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>25</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>200</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>50</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>M</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4758" style="width: 11.682em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.56em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.818em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4769"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4770" style="font-size: 70.7%; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-204-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>p</mi><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi>l</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mrow><mo>[</mo><msup><mi>H</mi><mo>+</mo></msup><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4784" style="width: 10.166em; <p>বিকল্প:</p>

font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4875" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4876" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4877" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4878" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4879" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">l</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.387em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -3.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.202em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>n</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>H</mi><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>50</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><msub><mi>n</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>N</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>H</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mfrac><mn>0.2</mn><mn>40</mn></mfrac><mn>0.2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>25</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>l</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-205">n_{HNO_3}=\left(50\times{10}^{-3}\times1\right)\ mol=50\times{10}^{-3}\ mol \\
n_{NaOH}=\frac{\frac{0.2}{40}}{0.2}=25\times{10}^{-3}\ mol 
</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-206-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>H</mi><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4880" style="width: 3.895em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-208-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><mi>H</mi><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>25</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>250</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi>p</mi><mi>H</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4926" style="width: 13.65em; </span>
            </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row question">
        <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 39 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>কোন বিক্রিয়ায়&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-209-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4967" style="width: 3.02em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.461em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1002.46em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.196em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4968"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4969"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.269em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute;             <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">

                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-5275"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5276"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5277" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">S<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-5280"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5281" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">O</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5282" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5283" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-5284" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.527em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1003.4em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.719em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5285"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5286" style="font-size: 70.7%; top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5291" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">25</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1003.53em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 3.527em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5292" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5293" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.2</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-5294" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5295" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">M<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.781em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -4.848em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>M</mi><mi>n</mi><msubsup><mi>O</mi><mn>4</mn><mo>−</mo></msubsup><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>F</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>H</mi><mo>+</mo></msup><mo stretchy="false">→</mo><mn>5</mn><mi>F</mi><msup><mi>e</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>3</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>M</mi><msup><mi>n</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>2</mn><mo>+</mo></mrow></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>4</mn><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi>O</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>K</mi><mi>M</mi><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mrow></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>M</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>K</mi><mi>M</mi><mi>n</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mrow><mn>1</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>F</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>S</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mrow></msub><mo>×</mo><msub><mi>M</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>F</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>S</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mrow><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>M</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi>F</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>S</mi><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>4</mn></msub></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>20</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.05</mn></mrow><mn>25</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>M</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-227">MnO_4^-+5Fe^{2+}+8H^+\rightarrow5Fe^{3+}+Mn^{2+}+4H_2O \\
\Rightarrow\frac{V_{KMnO_4}\times M_{KMnO_4}}{1}=\frac{V_{FeSO_4}\times M_{FeSO_4}}{5} \\
\Rightarrow M_{FeSO_4}=\frac{5\times20\times0.05}{25}=0.2\ M 
</script></span></p>
</span>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>

                        <span class="input-group-text" style="font-weight:bold;">D</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group-append questionTable">
                        <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>20%</p>
</label>
                   </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
            <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p>বিশুদ্ধ লোহা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-234-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mi>W</mi><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5416" style="width: 2.42em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.969em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1001.89em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5417"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5418" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5419" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">W<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.125em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5420" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.153em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mi>W</mi><mo>;</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-234">=W;</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-235-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mi>W</mi><mn>55.85</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>6</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.6755</mn><mi>g</mi><mi>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5421" style="width: 19.633em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 16.068em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1016.03em, 2.502em, -999.998em); margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5426" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">W<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.56em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.818em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5427" style="font-size: 70.7%; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.39em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.695em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5433" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1000</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.52em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-236-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5444" style="width: 0.658em; \therefore1\ mol\ CaCO_3\equiv2\ mol\ NaOH \\
\Rightarrow100\ g\ CaCO_3\equiv80\ g\ NaOH \\
\therefore24\ g\ CaCO_3\equiv\frac{80\times24}{100}=19.2\ g\ NaOH \\
S=\frac{n}{V}\Rightarrow V=\frac{n}{S}=\left(\frac{\frac{19.2}{40}}{0.8}\right)=0.6\ L=600\ mL 
</script></span></p>

                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-247-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5668" style="width: 12.953em; top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5669"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5670" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5671" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5674" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5675" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5676"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5677" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5678" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5679" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5680" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                 <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-249-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mi>M</mi></msub><msub><mi>V</mi><mi>M</mi></msub><mspace linebreak=&quot;newline&quot; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.289em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -4.447em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mi>M</mi></msub><msub><mi>V</mi><mi>M</mi></msub><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>S</mi><mi>M</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>50</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>50</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>0.1</mn></mrow><mn>250</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.32</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>M</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>∴</mo><mi>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>M</mi><mi>V</mi></mrow><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>0.32</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>40</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>250</mn></mrow><mn>1000</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3.2</mn><mi>g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-249">S_1V_1+S_2V_2+S_3V_3=S_MV_M \\
\Rightarrow S_M=\frac{50\times1+50\times0.5+50\times0.1}{250}=0.32\ M \\
\therefore W=\frac{SMV}{1000}=\frac{0.32\times40\times250}{1000}=3.2g 
</script></span></p>
</span>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 50 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>BOD পরীক্ষার জন্য একটি পুকুর থেকে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-250-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>d</mi><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5774" style="width: 3.132em;             <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p>আয়োডোমিতির সমীকরণ মতে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-259-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>L</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>N</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>N</mi><msub><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>O</mi><mn>3</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x2261;</mo><mn>8</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5858" style="width: 12.215em; <p>সুতরাং, অণুজীব যোগ করার পূর্বে&nbsp;50 mL পানিতে দ্রবীভূত অক্সিজেন&nbsp;1.6&nbsp;mg</p>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.781em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5969" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5970" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">≡</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5971" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-263-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5979" style="width: 0.658em; <p>সুতরাং,&nbsp;50&nbsp;mL&nbsp;পানি হতে হারানো অক্সিজেন&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-265-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1.6</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0.496</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>1.104</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5989" style="width: 13.855em; <p>অর্থাৎ,&nbsp;50 mL নমুনা পানির&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-266-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>B</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.104</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-6008" style="width: 7.625em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-267-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mn>1000</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-6018" style="width: 4.756em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-268-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>B</mi><mi>O</mi><mi>D</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1.104</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1000</mn></mrow><mn>50</mn></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>=</mo><mn>22.08</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi>m</mi><mi>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-6025" style="width: 14.756em; <p>সুতরাং, নমুনা পানির BOD হচ্ছে 22. 08 &nbsp;ppm</p>

                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 12 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p>আয়তন&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-33-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>22.4</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>16</mn></mrow><mn>32</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>11.2</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-610" style="width: 7.953em;                         <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-37-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2.5</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-650" style="width: 3.008em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.461em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.368em, 1002.42em, 2.325em, -999.998em); top: -2.184em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-651"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-652" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2.5</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-653" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-654" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">M</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.947em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>2.5</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-37">\rm 2.5\ M </script></span></p>

            <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-40-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>29</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>58</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>100</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-665" style="width: 8.199em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 6.723em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1006.48em, 2.502em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-669" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.789em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1002.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.35em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-670"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-671" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1000</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-672" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-673" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">29</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1002.3em, 4.141em, -999.998em);                 <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                <br>
                <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-62-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>{</mo><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C0;</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>}</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>B</mi><mo>.</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-923" style="width: 17.215em;
