            <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                <p><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong></p>

<p>15g চুনাপাথর ও HCl এসিডের বিক্রিয়ার ফলে 37°C তাপমাত্রায় ও <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-5-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>750</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>(</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>)</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-89" style="width: 6.634em;                         <span>Question 6 </span>

                    <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                        <p>প্রমাণ তাপমাত্রা ও চাপে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-7-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-109" style="width: 2.349em;                             <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-8-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>6.91</mn><mo>&amp;#xD7;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>22</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-115" style="width: 5.831em; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-212" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-213" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-214" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.952em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>760</mn><mo>×</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><mn>273</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>750</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2.53</mn></mrow><mn>310</mn></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>750</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>2.53</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>760</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>310</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2.2</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">L</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-12">\rm \frac{P_1V_1}{T_1}=\frac{P_2V_2}{T_2}\Rightarrow\frac{760\times V_1}{273}=\frac{750\times2.53}{310} \\ \rm \Rightarrow V_1=\frac{750\times2.53\times273}{760\times310}\therefore V_1=2.2\ L</script></span><br>

                    <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-16-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>22.4</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>L</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-263" style="width: 4.797em;     <div class="row questionBlock">
        <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
            <p><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong></p>

<p style="text-align: justify;">75g নমুনা লোহাকে অতিরিক্ত সালফিউরিক এসিডের সাথে সম্পূর্ণভাবে বিক্রিয়া করিয়ে 37°C তাপমাত্রায় ও 1 atm চাপে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-1-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>32</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1" style="width: 5.516em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.51em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.306em, 1004.51em, 2.498em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-2"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-3" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">32</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-5" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">d</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-6"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.269em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.43em, 1000.82em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-7" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.357em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-8" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-9" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-10"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.194em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.206em, 1000.71em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-11" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">H</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.747em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-12" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.225em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.275em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>32</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-1">\rm 32 \ dm^3 &nbsp;\ H_2</script></span> গ্যাস পাওয়া গেল।</p>

        </div>

    <div class="row question">
        <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 1 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                    <p>প্রমাণ তাপমাত্রা ও চাপে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-2-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-13" style="width: 1.567em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.269em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1001.27em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.196em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-14"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-15"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.269em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.206em, 1000.9em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-16" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">H<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.076em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-17" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.2em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.225em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.093em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-2">H_2</script></span> গ্যাসে পরমাণুর সংখ্যা কত?</p>

vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><mn>273</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>32</mn></mrow><mn>310</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>28.18</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-7">\rm \frac{P_1V_1}{T_1}=\frac{P_2V_2}{T_2}\Rightarrow\frac{1\times V_1}{273}=\frac{1\times32}{310}\Rightarrow V_1=28.18\ dm^3</script></span><br>
∴ পরমাণুর সংখ্যা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-8-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>28.18</mn><mn>22.4</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msub><mi>N</mi><mi>A</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1.51</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>24</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-106" style="width: 13.404em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.986em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1010.99em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-107"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-108" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-109" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-110" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-111" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.723em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.6em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.818em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-112" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">28.18</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.23em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.613em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-113" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">22.4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.72em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.723em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-114" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-115" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.395em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.9em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-116" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">N<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-117" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">A</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-118" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-119" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.51</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-120" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-125"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-126"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-127" style="font-size: 70.7%;             <div class="row">
                <div class="serial">
                    <span>Question 3 </span>
                </div>
                <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
